2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Fjob%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22job%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23job%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Fmusic%2Foriginal-sound-7360007609216289566%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%E2%99%AC%20original%20sound%20-%20svvampfae%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%99%AC%20original%20sound%20-%20svvampfae%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fsection%3E%20%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%3EIt%20depends%20on%20the%20role%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20a%20third%20(32%25)%20of%20people%20in%20the%20US%20have%20a%20tattoo%2C%20and%2022%25%20have%20more%20than%20one%2C%20according%20to%20Pew%20Research%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20studies%20have%20suggested%20that%20tattoos%20can%20affect%20someone's%20career%20progression.%20In%202018%2C%20a%20LinkedIn%20survey%20found%20that%2040%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20had%20rejected%20a%20candidate%20for%20a%20job%20because%20they%20had%20a%20visible%20tattoo.%2088%25%20of%20recruiters%20and%20HR%20professionals%20who%20responded%20said%20they%20thought%20tattoos%20limited%20a%20candidate's%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20research%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Miami%20that%20same%20year%20found%20tattooed%20job-seekers%20were%20no%20less%20likely%20to%20be%20employed%20than%20those%20without.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stigma%20of%20tattoos%20is%20lessening%20every%20day%2C%20with%20many%20employers%20no%20longer%20having%20an%20issue%20with%20hiring%20tattooed%20employees%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indeed.com%2Fhire%2Fc%2Finfo%2Ftattoos-in-the-workplace-considerations-and-policies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Indeed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20may%20still%20be%20a%20line%2C%20though%2C%20and%20some%20viewers%20argued%20that%20Putnam%20crossed%20it.%20Putnam%20didn't%20comment%20on%20the%20record%20for%20this%20article%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Fwoman-denied-job-tk-maxx-32643836%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe%20told%20the%20UK%20publication%20The%20Daily%20Star%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20going%20to%20change%20who%20I%20am%20for%20minimum%20wage%20jobs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdam%20Collins%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20at%20Ignite%20SEO%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20as%20someone%20who%20hires%20people%20to%20work%20at%20his%20company%2C%20%26quot%3Btattoos%20can%20make%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20how%20a%20candidate%20is%20perceived.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20say%20that%20tattoos%20make%20or%20break%20an%20interview%20because%20it%20depends%20on%20the%20role%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20candidate%20applying%20to%20be%20an%20account%20manager%20for%20our%20clients%20and%20is%20supposed%20to%20speak%20to%20our%20clients%20directly%20should%20definitely%20appear%20trustworthy%20and%20clean-cut%2C%20so%20face%20and%20neck%20tattoos%20would%20affect%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20with%20someone%20who%20isn't%20directly%20working%20with%20clients%2C%20appearance%20is%20less%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20technical%20and%20operational%20roles%2C%20for%20example%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20not%20a%20big%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichelle%20Enjoli%2C%20a%20career%20coach%2C%20told%20BI%20the%20visibility%20and%20type%20of%20tattoos%20someone%20has%20can%20make%20a%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTattoos%20are%20personal%20and%20typically%20represent%20something%20for%20that%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20represent%20companies%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20if%20a%20tattoo%20represents%20something%20that%20a%20company%20would%20not%20want%20to%20be%20associated%20with%2C%20it%20can%20definitely%20be%20an%20issue%20for%20a%20hiring%20manager.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20likely%20it%20is%20that%20a%20tattoo%20will%20make%20or%20break%20an%20interview%20depends%20on%20how%20visible%20they%20are%20and%20what%20they%20may%20represent%2C%20Enjoli%20added.%20Tattoos%20are%20nowhere%20near%20as%20much%20of%20a%20taboo%20as%20they%20used%20to%20be%2C%20but%20some%20people%20still%20hold%20judgment%20over%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Putnam's%20case%2C%20her%20tattoos%20were%20considered%20extreme%2C%20Enjoli%20said%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bseemed%20to%20be%20a%20big%20part%20of%20her%20identity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20other%20cases%20where%20someone%20might%20have%20a%20smaller%20tattoo%20on%20their%20arm%20or%20visible%20area%2C%20it%20might%20not%20matter%20as%20much%20as%20it%20is%20less%20obvious%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20company%20demanding%20that%20an%20employee%20not%20have%20any%20tattoos%20regardless%20of%20visibility%20or%20meaning%20is%20definitely%20outdated%20as%20they%20have%20become%20a%20big%20part%20of%20the%20modern%20culture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPersonality%20matters%20more%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJustina%20Raskauskiene%2C%20the%20HR%20team%20lead%20at%20Omnisend%2C%20told%20BI%20as%20tattoos%20have%20become%20more%20common%2C%20it's%20likely%20recruiters%20and%20hiring%20managers%20barely%20pay%20attention%20to%20them%20%26quot%3Bunless%20they%20are%20offensive%20or%20distracting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20hiring%20managers%20may%20even%20prefer%20an%20employee%20with%20a%20tattoo%20because%20it%20can%20be%20evidence%20of%20an%20interesting%20personality%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDiscriminating%20against%20those%20people%20would%20mean%20missing%20out%20on%20some%20talented%20people%20in%20the%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERachel%20Pelta%2C%20the%20head%20writer%20at%20virtual%20work%20experience%20platform%20Forage%20told%20BI%20that%20overall%2C%20hiring%20managers%20are%20looking%20at%20skills%20and%20abilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20is%2C%20everyone%20who's%20interviewing%20probably%20has%20the%20skills%20and%20abilities%20I'm%20looking%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20then%20it%20comes%20down%20to%2C%20how%20well%20are%20you%20selling%20yourself%20in%20the%20interview%3F%20Are%20you%20making%20the%20case%20for%20why%20you're%20the%20best%20person%20for%20the%20role%3F%20If%20you're%20not%20doing%20that%2C%20you%20won't%20get%20the%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20tattoos%2C%20piercings%2C%20or%20anything%20else%20that%20could%20be%20considered%20unusual%2C%20such%20as%20bright%20hair%20colors%2C%20hiring%20managers%20%26quot%3Bshouldn't%20evaluate%20a%20candidate%20on%20their%20appearance%2C%26quot%3B%20Pelta%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20companies%20are%20traditional%20or%20conservative%2C%20and%20for%20them%2C%20these%20things%20could%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20deal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnless%20you're%20willing%20to%20cover%20or%20remove%20them%2C%20you'll%20have%20to%20keep%20searching%20until%20you%20find%20a%20company%20that%20accepts%20you%20as%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20they%20are%20out%20there%2C%20it%20just%20may%20take%20you%20a%20bit%20longer%20to%20find%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftattoos-shouldnt-be-important-in-job-interviews-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713951923000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6626465623b29110d3014e77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftattoos-shouldnt-be-important-in-job-interviews-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20heavily-tattooed%20creator's%20video%20sparked%20a%20debate%20on%20social%20media%20about%20how%20much%20of%20an%20issue%20tattoos%20are%20to%20hiring%20managers%20and%20in%20job%20interviews.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ldodgson%40insider.com%20(Lindsay%20Dodgson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22ca