0of%20his%20Tesla%20stock%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20buy%20Twitter%2C%20tried%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitter-to-take-elon-musk-court-fight-close-deal-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eget%20out%20of%20the%20deal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20then%20was%20forced%20to%20go%20through%20with%20it.%20He%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-starship-launch-rocket-blows-up-explosion-elon-musk-mars-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eblew%20up%20some%20rockets%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(to%20be%20fair%2C%20some%20also%20made%20it%20to%20space).%20He%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-neuralink-monkeys-live-in-paradise-denies-gruesome-deaths-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eimplanted%20a%20brain%20chip%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20into%20a%20bunch%20of%20monkeys.%20He%20brought%20a%20kitchen%20sink%20to%20work%20and%20added%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-twitter-tesla-ceo-job-broken-chief-hypocrisy-officer-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efew%20more%20CEO%20jobs%20to%20his%20plate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20He%20publicly%20bungled%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis'%20attempt%20to%20launch%20a%20presidential%20campaign.%20At%20Tesla%2C%20Musk%20delivered%20about%204%2C000%20Cybertrucks%20%E2%80%94%20every%20one%20of%20which%20has%20been%20recalled%20for%20faulty%20acceleration%20%E2%80%94%20while%20frittering%20away%20any%20goodwill%20the%20company%20has%20with%20its%20core%20customers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20I'm%20saying%20is%20that%20as%20much%20as%20Tesla%20accomplished%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20it's%20clear%20Musk%20should've%20spent%20more%20time%20with%20it.%20Tesla%20failed%20to%20craft%20a%20strategy%20for%20chaotic%20times%20in%20what%20is%20still%20clearly%20a%20nascent%20EV%20industry.%20Sure%2C%20the%20company%20has%20been%20on%20a%20multiyear%20campaign%20to%20get%20lean%20and%20cut%20costs%2C%20but%20that%20strategy%20isn't%20enough%20to%20balance%20out%20price%20cuts%2C%20weak%20demand%2C%20and%20the%20need%20for%20major%20capital%20expenditures%20to%20get%20through%20this%20period%20of%20fleet%20stagnation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20true%20visionary%20CEO%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Musk%20has%20long%20claimed%20to%20be%20%E2%80%94%20would%20have%20pressed%20the%20advantage%20that%20Tesla%20developed%20in%20the%20EV%20market.%20They%20would've%20done%20research%20to%20try%20to%20understand%20what%20EV%20demand%20would%20look%20like%20after%20early%20adopters%20bought%20cars.%20They'd%20know%20what%20kinds%20of%20buyers%20would%20enter%20the%20market%20at%20that%20stage%2C%20and%20which%20kinds%20of%20cars%20those%20buyers%20would%20want.%20A%20true%20visionary%20CEO%20would%20meet%20those%20customers%20where%20they%20are.%20Back%20in%20November%2C%20I%20spoke%20with%20Navdeep%20Sodhi%2C%20a%20pricing%20analyst%20at%20Sodhi%20Pricing%20Associates%2C%20who%20told%20me%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-price-cuts-electric-cars-losing-business-strategy-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETesla%20should%20advertise%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20educate%20the%20public%20about%20the%20cost%20benefits%20of%20its%20cars%2C%20like%20savings%20on%20gas.%20Advertising%20could%20have%20also%20helped%20assuage%20concerns%20about%20issues%20like%20range%20anxiety.%20This%20month%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-new-marketing-team-advertising-cut-layoffs-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETesla%20laid%20off%20its%20entire%20marketing%20team%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20years%20analysts%20warned%20Musk%20that%20competition%20was%20coming%2C%20not%20just%20from%20legacy%20automakers%20but%20from%20the%20very%20Chinese%20market%20that%20fostered%20Tesla's%20success.%20Beijing%20has%20a%20pattern%20of%20supporting%20Western%20companies%20in%20China's%20markets%20in%20order%20to%20foster%20competition%2C%20then%2C%20once%20China-based%20rivals%20are%20able%20to%20catch%20up%2C%20tipping%20the%20scales%20in%20favor%20of%20homegrown%20companies.%20Add%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20Beijing%20has%20cornered%20nearly%20every%20aspect%20of%20the%20battery%20supply%20chain%20%E2%80%94%20from%20mining%20and%20refining%20metals%20to%20manufacturing%20the%20batteries%20themselves%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20helped%20China's%20EV%20makers%20to%20churn%20out%20models%20at%20price%20points%20as%20low%20as%20four%20figures.%20The%20new%20options%20have%20put%20Tesla%20on%20the%20back%20foot%20in%20one%20of%20its%20most%20important%20markets%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftesla-stock-vehicle-model-y-price-cuts-tsla-elon-musk-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETesla's%20share%20of%20China's%20car%20market%20shrank%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%206.7%25%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202023%20from%2010.3%25%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20maintain%20its%20lead%2C%20Tesla%20should%20have%20been%20singularly%20focused%20on%20building%20the%20Model%202%20%E2%80%94%20moving%20down%20the%20pricing%20scale%20to%20where%20there%20were%20more%20customers.%20But%20it%20stopped%20innovating%2C%20the%20Model%202%20hasn't%20materialized%2C%20and%20Musk's%20realization%20that%20the%20company%20needs%20to%20deliver%20a%20Tesla-for-the-people%20may%20be%20coming%20too%20late.%20Instead%20of%20boosting%20sales%20with%20an%20impressive%20or%20accessible%20new%20option%2C%20Tesla%20has%20tried%20to%20goose%20demand%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-slashes-prices-suv-cars-self-driving-software-before-earnings-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eerratically%20lowering%20the%20prices%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20its%20existing%20models%20to%20increase%20volume.%20This%20has%20not%20worked%20as%20planned%3A%20automotive%20revenue%20fell%2013%25%20from%20the%20same%20time%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20Tuesday's%20earnings%20release%2C%20and%20gross%20margins%20in%20the%20automotive%20division%20fell%20to%2014.8%25%20from%2018%25%20a%20year%20before.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETesla%20has%20always%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bgrowth%26quot%3B%20company%2C%20the%20up-and-coming%20player%20taking%20on%20the%20legacy%20automakers.%20But%20now%20the%20company%20has%20entered%20a%20new%20stage%20of%20development%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20large%2C%20mature%20firm%2C%20and%20continuing%20to%20grow%20requires%20larger%20amounts%20of%20capital%2C%20discipline%2C%20and%20focus.%20There%20was%20never%20a%20moment%20for%20Musk%20to%20rest%20on%20his%20laurels%2C%20but%20after%202020%20Tesla%20started%20to%20look%20less%20like%20a%20place%20where%20Musk%20pushed%20constant%20automotive%20innovation%20and%20more%20like%20a%20place%20where%20Musk%20sourced%20cash%20to%20do%20whatever%20else%20he%20wanted%20with%20his%20life.%20Maybe%20he%20got%20bored%2C%20or%20maybe%20he%20got%20distracted%20%E2%80%94%20either%20way%2C%20Musk%20stopped%20pushing%20the%20envelope%20at%20Tesla%20way%20too%20early.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20conference%20call%2C%20Musk%20had%20a%20million%20excuses%20for%20why%20this%20quarter%20was%20so%20poor%20%E2%80%94%20Houthi%20agitation%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20an%20arson%20in%20Berlin%2C%20updates%20at%20the%20Fremont%20Factory.%20He%20asserted%20that%20Tesla%20was%20not%20a%20car%20company%20but%20rather%20an%20AI%20robotics%20comp