%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%20is%20among%20the%20four%20states%20where%20Assembly%20polls%20are%20being%20held%20alongside%20the%20general%20election.%20Mr%20Naidu's%20TDP%20has%20tied%20up%20with%20the%20BJP%20to%20take%20on%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy's%20YSCRP%2C%20which%20scored%20a%20thumping%20win%20in%20the%202019%20state%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20at%20Srikakulam%2C%20Mr%20Naidu%20said%20TDP%20is%20doing%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20well%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20has%20no%20doubt%20about%20a%20good%20show.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20numbers.%20People%20have%20decided%2C%20people%20have%20realised%20what%20they%20have%20lost%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20Now%20I%20am%20seeing%20the%20response.%20This%20is%20my%2010th%20election.%20Today%2C%20there%20is%20an%20extraordinary%20response.%20Every%20section%20of%20people%20is%20annoyed%2C%20frustrated.%20They%20want%20to%20protect%20the%20state.%20It%20is%20not%20my%20election%2C%20it%20is%20the%20election%20of%20the%20five%20crore%20people%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20their%20future%20and%20the%20future%20of%20their%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20his%20government%20was%20voted%20out%2C%20Mr%20Naidu%20had%20started%20building%20Amaravati%20into%20the%20new%20capital%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20after%20the%20state%20was%20bifurcated%20to%20create%20Telangana.%20Work%2C%20however%2C%20slowed%20down%20after%20Mr%20Reddy%20took%20over%20and%20decided%20to%20develop%20three%20capital%20cities%20--%20Amaravati%20as%20legislative%20capital%2C%20Visakhapatnam%20as%20executive%20capital%20and%20Kurnool%20as%20judicial%20capital.%20The%20proposal%20was%20challenged%20in%20court%2C%20and%20the%20High%20Court%20struck%20it%20down.%20The%20YSRCP%20government%20has%20now%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%20chief%20said%20the%20uncertainty%20over%20a%20capital%20city%20is%20among%20the%20most%20important%20issues%20in%20this%20election.%20%26quot%3BA%20capital%20is%20very%20important.%20Tamil%20Nadu%20can%20proudly%20say%20Chennai%2C%20Telangana%20can%20say%20Hyderabad%2C%20Karnataka%20Bangalore.%20After%2010%20years%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20an%20address%2C%20which%20is%20our%20capital%3F%20Jagan%20(Mohan%20Reddy)%20is%20saying%20three%20capitals.%20Has%20it%20been%20successful%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20betrayed%20the%20people%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20%26quot%3BBifurcation%20is%20a%20painful%20process.%20But%2C%20the%20five-year%20rule%20of%20Jagan%20Mohan%20reddy%20has%20done%20more%20damage%20than%20bifurcation.%20My%20duty%20is%20to%20protect%20the%20state%20and%20its%20future.%20I%20laid%20a%20very%20strong%20foundation%20for%20Hyderabad%20and%20wealth%20was%20created.%20Here%2C%20in%20Amarvati%2C%20I%20got%20everything%20done%2C%20but%20he%20destroyed%20the%20future%20of%20Andhra%20in%20the%20name%20of%20three%20capitals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDP's%20return%20to%20the%20NDA%20comes%20six%20years%20after%20a%20bitter%20separation%20over%20Mr%20Naidu's%20demand%20for%20a%20special%20status%20for%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Asked%20about%20his%20return%20to%20the%20NDA%20fold%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20tried%20to%20get%20special%20status%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20happen.%20But%20I%20got%20so%20many%20things%2C%2011%20all-India%20institutes%20of%20education%20and%20health%2C%20IIT%2C%20IIM%2C%20IISER%2C%20NIT%2C%20AIIMS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20(Centre)%20gave%20money%2C%20clearances%20for%20Amravati%2C%20capital%20gains%20exemption%20for%20farmers%2C%20all%20this%20I%20got%2C%20and%20today%2C%20we%20have%20lost%20everything.%20But%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20vision%20and%20my%20experience%2C%20we%20will%20make%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20the%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20planning%20for%202047.%20%26quot%3BHe%20wants%20to%20make%20India%20and%20Indians%20no%201%20globally.%20We%20want%20to%20coordinate%20with%20the%20central%20government%20and%20fulfil%20aspirations%20of%20the%20Telugu%20community%2C%20that%20is%20my%20dream.%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20we%20will%20do%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Naidu%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20stressed%20that%20the%20state's%20economy%20is%20in%20bad%20shape%20due%20to%20the%20YSRCP%20government's%20policies.%20%26quot%3BBluffing%20the%20poor%20is%20not%20the%20correct%20approach%2C%20creation%20of%20wealth%20is%20important%2C%20you%20have%20to%20balance%20welfare%20and%20development%2C%20only%20then%20will%20there%20will%20be%20a%20sustainable%20ecosystem.%20Now%20it's%20corruption%20and%20looting%20the%20state.%20Opportunities%20have%20been%20destroyed.%20All%20institutions%20have%20been%20destabilised%2C%20this%20is%20chaos.%20Government%20properties%20have%20been%20mortgaged.%20He%20(Reddy)%20is%20thinking%20only%20about%20today%2C%20not%20tomorrow.%20He%20has%20borrowed%2013%20lakh%20crores%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20question%20on%20the%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20against%20him%2C%20the%20TDP%20chief%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCould%20they%20produce%20even%20one%20piece%20of%20evidence%3F%20Political%20victimisation%20is%20different.%20He%20(Reddy)%20has%20a%20vast%20track%20record.%20He%20wanted%20to%20throw%20mud%20at%20me%2C%20he%20is%20trying%20his%20best%2C%20but%20the%20nation%20knows%20my%20character.%20For%2045%20years%2C%20I%20have%20survived%20in%20politics%20for%20my%20credibility%2C%20honesty%2C%20integrity.%20No%20one%20can%20question%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Naidu%20was%20also%20asked%20about%20the%20Congress's%20claims%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20is%20a%20no%20factor%20as%20far%20as%20elections%20in%20south%20India%20are%20concerned.%20%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20has%20changed.%20Earlier%2C%20regional%20parties%20were%20dominant.%20People%20are%20thinking%20differently%20now.%20Local%20leadership%20with%20strong%20national%20leadership%20will%20help%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20recent%20incident%20in%20which%20a%20stone%20was%20thrown%20at%20Chief%20Minister%20Reddy%2C%20leaving%20him%20injured%2C%20Mr%20Naidu%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20a%20habitual%20liar.%20A%20small%20stone%20that%20is%20not%20visible%20or%20traceable%2C%20and%20he%20is%20claiming%20an%20assassination%20attempt.%20This%20is%20just%20drama%2C%20every%20election%20he%20needs%20drama.%20He%20is%20a%20good%20drama%20actor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713949860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Flqkuc2lg_chandrababu-naidu_625x300_24_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fn-chandrababu-naidu-jagan-mohan-reddy-2024-andhra-pradesh-election-drama-every-election-chandrababu-naidu-on-stone-attack-on-jagan-reddy-5511883%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20YS%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20has%20betrayed%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20and%20destroyed%20their%20future%2C%20his%20predecessor%20and%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20president%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fn-chandrababu-naidu-jagan-mohan-reddy-2024-andhra-pradesh-election-drama-every-election-chandrababu-naidu-on-stone-attack-on-jagan-reddy-5511883%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20Were%20Not%20Comfortable%26quot%3B%3A%20CSK%20Coach's%20Interesting%20Take%20On%20Loss%20vs%20LSG%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20side's%20six-wicket%20loss%20to%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%2C%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20(CSK)%20head%20coach%20Stephen%20Fleming%20said%20that%20the%20team%20is%20not%20focusing%20on%20finding%20a%20quick%20fix%20to%20their%20problems%2C%20but%20rather%20a%20right%20combination%20that%20will%20contribute%20during%20the%20back-end%20of%20the%20tournament.%20Marcus%20Stoinis%20defied%20the%20odds%20with%20his%20relentless%20onslaught%20and%20his%20maiden%20ton%20guided%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20to%20a%206-wicket%20win%20over%20the%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20at%20Chepauk%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20game%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference%2C%20Fleming%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20a%20little%20bit%20uncomfortable%20with%20some%20areas.%20So%2C%20we%20are%20just%20trying%20to%20find%20not%20a%20quick%20fix%2C%20but%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20find%20the%20right%20combination%20where%20players%20are%20going%20to%20contribute%20for%20the%20back%20end%20of%20this%20tournament.%20We%20have%20had%20injuries%2C%20and%20we%20have%20been%20a%20little%20bit%20unsettled%2C%20but%20the%20main%20thing%20is%20getting%20guys%20in%20key%20areas%20and%20in%20form%20and%20that%20sometimes%20takes%20a%20bit%20of%20time.%20But%20yeah%2C%20there%20has%20been%20more%20change.%20Some%20of%20it%20is%20forced%20upon%20us%20and%20some%20of%20it%20is%20form.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20more%20about%20the%20game%2C%20Fleming%20said%20that%20the%20team%20knew%20that%20dew%20was%20going%20to%20come%20after%2020-25%20overs%20of%20surface%20being%20slow%20so%20the%20toss%20was%20important.%20He%20also%20lauded%20the%20skipper%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20and%20LSG%20all-rounder%20Marcus%20Stoinis%20for%20their%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20a%20great%20hundred%20from%20Ruturaj%2C%20absolute%20craft%2C%20fantastic%20knock%20and%20he%20played%20incredibly%20well%20with%20some%20power%20to%20get%20us%20to%20a%20score%20of%20210.%20So%2C%20we%20were%20not%20comfortable%20with%20that%20score%2C%20but%20we%20knew%20we%20were%20in%20the%20game.%20And%20we%20saw%20another%20great%20hundred%20from%20Marcus%20Stoinis.%20So%2C%20they%20answered%20pretty%20well.%20And%20in%20the%20end%2C%20it%20was%20a%20good%20game%20of%20cricket.%20We%20felt%20we%20competed%20well%2C%20given%20the%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20went%20on%20to%20laud%20Stoinis%20further%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20he%20has%20got%20%26quot%3Bpower%20and%20good%20batsmanship%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(LSG)%20needed%20someone%20to%20do%20what%20Ruturaj%20did%20and%20Stoinis%20did%20that%20beautifully.%20But%20not%20a%20surprise%2C%20we%20knew%20he%20is%20a%20danger%20weapon%2C%20a%20dangerous%20player%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20get%20him%20out%20with%20Pooran%20and%20the%20other%20two%20at%20the%20top.%20So%2C%20we%20got%20close%20but%20we%20just%20could%20not%20get%20the%20last%20one%20out.%20Good%20game%20though%20and%20again%20two%20great%20hundreds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20former%20skipper%20and%20legendary%20wicketkeeper-batter%20MS%20Dhoni's%20reception%20on%20the%20crease%2C%20Fleming%20said%20that%20the%20franchise%20and%20the%20fans%20are%20really%20lucky%20to%20have%20experienced%20Dhoni's%20%26quot%3Bmagic%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20last%2016-17%20years%20or%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20I%20said%20it%20earlier%2C%20but%20the%20love%20for%20him%20throughout%20India%20and%20throughout%20the%20world%20is%20testimony%20to%20the%20way%20he's%20played%20the%20game.%20People%20talk%20about%20MS%20as%20a%20person%2C%20but%20he%20is%20also%20a%20great%20player%20and%20he%20has%20done%20some%20great%20things%20for%20India%20and%20for%20Chennai.%20So%2C%20people%20were%20just%20taking%20time%20and%20energy%20and%20effort%20to%20appreciate%20him%20and%20we%20do%20that%20every%20day.%20And%20we%20are%20very%20lucky%20to%20have%20him%20in%20the%20side%20for%20so%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Fleming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFleming%20also%20said%20that%20the%20batting%20all-rounder%20Shivam%20Dube%2C%20who%20has%20not%20bowled%20since%20IPL%202022%2C%20has%20been%20working%20really%20hard%20on%20his%20bowling%20for%20the%20last%2012-18%20months%20and%20is%20aware%20of%20how%20important%20he%20is%20as%20a%20bowler.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20knows%20the%20importance%20of%20him%20bowling.%20So%2C%20he%20is%20working%20very%20hard%20on%20that.%20It%20has%20not%20transpired%20for%20him%20to%20have%20overs%20in%20the%20games%20just%20yet%2C%20but%20he%20is%20working%20very%20hard%20on%20that.%20And%20what%20he%20is%20also%20working%20hard%20is%20his%20batsmanship.%20And%20I%20think%20that%20has%20been%20a%20real%20area%20of%20improvement%20in%20the%20last%2012%20to%2018%20months.%20Again%2C%20today%20he%20was%20a%20lot%20more%20comfortable%20against%20quicker%20bowling%2C%20but%20he%20still%20has%20that%20power%2C%20which%20is%20quite%20unique%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Fleming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20been%20a%20good%2C%20consistent%20performer%20for%20us%20this%20season.%20And%20I%20think%20to%20win%20the%20IPL%20you%20need%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20that%2C%20a%20bit%20of%20magic%20sprinkled%20throughout%20and%20he%20is%20providing%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20concluded%20Fleming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ongoing%20season%2C%20Shivam%20Dube%20is%20the%20sixth-highest%20run-getter.%20He%20has%20scored%20311%20runs%20in%20eight%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2051.83%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20169.94%2C%20with%20three%20half-centuries.%20His%20best%20score%20is%2066*.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20LSG%20opted%20to%20bowl%20first.%20After%20a%20slow%20start%2C%20it%20was%20a%20century%20from%20skipper%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20(108%20in%2060%20balls%2C%20with%2012%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes)%20and%20an%20explosive%20half-century%20from%20in-form%20Shivam%20Dube%20(66%20in%2027%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20seven%20sixes)%20that%20powered%20CSK%20to%20210%2F4%20in%20their%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatt%20Henry%2C%20Mohsin%20Khan%20and%20Yash%20Thakur%20got%20a%20wicket%20each%20for%20LSG.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run-chase%2C%20LSG%20struggled%20to%20catch%20the%20right%20tempo%20in%20the%20first%20half%20and%20was%2088%2F3%20in%2011%20overs.%20But%20it%20was%20Stoinis%2C%20who%20was%20sent%20up%20the%20order%2C%20kept%20his%20side%20in%20the%20hunt%20with%20his%20ferocious%20striking.%20Cameos%20from%20Nicholas%20Pooran%20(34%20in%2015%20balls%2C%20with%20six%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%20and%20Deepak%20Hooda%20(17*%20in%20six%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20relieved%20some%20pressure%20from%20the%20Aussie%20star's%20shoulders%20as%20he%20blasted%2017%20runs%20within%20three%20balls%20of%20the%20final%20over%20to%20seal%20a%20six-wicket%20win.%20Stoinis%20was%20unbeaten%20on%20124%20in%2063%20balls%2C%20with%2013%20fours%20and%20six%20sixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStoinis%20took%20home%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELSG%20is%20in%20the%20fourth%20spot%20with%20five%20wins%20and%20three%20losses%2C%20giving%20them%2010%20points.%20CSK%20has%20dropped%20to%20fifth%20spot%2C%20with%20four%20wins%2C%20four%20losses%20and%20a%20total%20of%20eight%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713949860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F4ncsnud_stephen-fleming-bcci_625x300_24_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fwe-were-not-comfortable-csk-coach-stephen-fleming-interesting-take-on-loss-against-lsg-5511548%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Following%20the%20game%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference%2C%20Fleming%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20a%20little%20bit%20uncomf