ing%20overseas.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPhones%20use%20satellite%20maritime%20cellular%2C%20and%20it's%20ridiculously%20expensive.%20I've%20heard%20of%20people%20who%20have%20come%20home%20with%20%241%2C000%20cellular%20bills%20because%20they%20didn't%20turn%20off%20their%20roaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20typically%20make%20most%20of%20my%20calls%20over%20WiFi%2C%20but%20you%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20on%20some%20ships.%20Texting%20from%20ship%20to%20land%20usually%20works%20well%20if%20you're%20using%20the%20same%20type%20of%20phone%20as%20the%20person%20you're%20messaging%2C%20but%20when%20you're%20texting%20cross-platform%2C%20sometimes%20it%20doesn't%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinding%20power%20outlets%20can%20be%20challenging%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20laptop%20plugged%20into%20an%20outlet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6627cb6010dfcda409621d41%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221326%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOutlets%20on%20the%20Scarlet%20Lady.%3Cp%3EWalter%20Biscardi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20if%20you%20need%20to%20put%20in%20a%20full%20day%20of%20work%20connected%20to%20power%2C%20you%20need%20to%20stay%20in%20your%20room.%20One%20tip%20to%20finding%20power%20when%20you're%20looking%20around%20public%20areas%20is%20to%20see%20where%20they%20plug%20in%20the%20vacuum%20cleaners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20strongly%20recommend%20bringing%20a%20powerboard%20with%20multiple%20USB%20sockets.%20I%20have%20one%20with%2010%20USB%20connections%2C%20so%20I%20can%20charge%20my%20phone%2C%20GoPro%2C%20and%20other%20devices%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EVirgin%20Voyages%20ships%20are%20the%20most%20friendly%20for%20remote%20workers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20galley%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirgin-voyages-cruise-ship-best-food-restaurants-2024-4