ider%C2%A0than%20those%20in%20Europe%20or%20America.%20It%20also%C2%A0revealed%C2%A0that%C2%A0the%20current%20footwear%20sizing%20system%20has%20many%20Indians%20wearing%20shoes%20that%20are%20either%20too%20large%20or%20have%20poor%20fitting.%20The%20survey%20further%20found%20that%20the%20average%20foot%20size%20growth%20for%20Indian%20women%20peaked%20at%2011%20years%20old%2C%20while%20for%20Indian%20men%2C%20it%20peaked%20at%20around%2015%20or%2016%20years%20old.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%C2%A0revealed%20that%20shoelaces%C2%A0were%20often%20tightened%C2%A0excessively%2C%20disrupting%20normal%20blood%20flow%20for%20the%20wearer%2C%20which%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20led%20to%20discomfort%2C%20injuries%2C%20and%20foot%20health%20issues%2C%20especially%20among%C2%A0the%20elderly%C2%A0and%20people%20with%20diabetes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EAbout%20the%C2%A0%E2%80%98Bha'%C2%A0system%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0'Bha'%C2%A0shoe%20sizing%20system%20is%C2%A0a%C2%A0simplified%C2%A0approach%C2%A0with%C2%A0%3Cwbr%3E8%C2%A0footwear%20sizes%20suited%20to%20fit%20different%20age%20groups.%C2%A0It%20aims%20to%20provide%20a%20better%20fit%20for%20about%2085%25%20of%20Indians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%C2%A0is%20expected%C2%A0to%20simplify%20manufacturing%20by%20eliminating%20half-sizes.%20It%20also%20promises%20increased%20comfort%2C%C2%A0%20increased%20comfort%2C%20wider%20dimensions%20and%20an%20additional%205mm%20allowance%20for%20foot%20length.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%E2%80%98Bha'%C2%A0shoe%20sizing%20system%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0'Bha'%C2%A0shoe%20sizing%20system%20introduces%C2%A08%C2%A0sizes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20%E2%80%93%20Infants%20(0-1%20year)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EII%20%E2%80%93%20Toddlers%20(1-3%20years)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIII%20%E2%80%93%20Small%20children%20(4-6%20years)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIV%20%E2%80%93%20Children%20(7-11%20years)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EV%20%E2%80%93%20Girls%20(12-13%20years)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVI%20%E2%80%93%20Boys%20(12-14%20years)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVII%20%E2%80%93%20Women%20(14%20years%20and%20above)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVIII%20%E2%80%93%20Men%20(15%20years%20and%20above)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProduction%20will%20primarily%20focus%20on%20sizes%20III%20to%20VIII%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20needs%20of%C2%A0the%20majority%20of%C2%A0Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713947280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-10%2Fleather-shoe-reuters_650x400_61507099296.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-bha-the-new-shoe-sizing-system-for-indians-5511665%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20footwear%20sizing%20system%2C%20specifically%20designed%20for%20Indians%2C%20is%20in%20the%20works.%20Named%20'Bha'%20for%20'Bharat'%2C%20it%20aims%20to%20replace%20existing%20UK%2FEuropean%20and%20US%20sizes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-bha-the-new-shoe-sizing-system-for-indians-5511665%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-bha-the-new-shoe-sizing-system-for-indians-5511665%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-bha-the-new-shoe-sizing-system-for-indians-5511665%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Has%20Congress%20Promised%20'Wealth%20Redistribution'%20In%20Manifesto%3F%20A%20Fact%20Check%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20political%20row%20has%20broken%20out%20over%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-distances-itself-from-sam-pitrodas-remarks-on-wealth-distribution-5510493%5C%22%3ESam%20Pitroda's%20remarks%20on%20inheritance%20tax%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20claiming%20that%20this%20was%20a%20sign%20that%20the%20party%2C%20if%20voted%20to%20power%2C%20will%20redistribute%20the%20wealth%20of%20Indians.%20Mr%20Pitroda's%20example%20of%20an%20inheritance%20tax%20in%20the%20US%20added%20fuel%20to%20the%20fire%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20douse%20since%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20raised%20the%20issue%20at%20a%20rally%20two%20days%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Congress%20distanced%20itself%20from%20the%20remarks%2C%20Mr%20Pitroda%20also%20issued%20a%20clarification%20today%20saying%20that%20he%20was%20just%20expressing%20his%20views%20on%20the%20inheritance%20tax%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20what%20I%20said%20as%20an%20individual%20on%20inheritance%20tax%20in%20the%20US%20is%20twisted%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20what%20lies%20PM%20is%20spreading%20about%20Congress%20manifesto%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pitroda%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20targeted%20the%20Congress%20claiming%20that%20the%20party's%20manifesto%20promises%20to%20seize%20and%20redistribute%20the%20wealth%20of%20Indians%2C%20a%20charge%20it%20denies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20Congress%20manifesto%20says.%20They%20will%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20gold%20that%20(our)%20mothers%20and%20sisters%20have%2C%20they%20will%20count%20and%20assess%20it%2C%20and%20then%20they%20will%20distribute%20that%20wealth%2C%20and%20they%20will%20give%20it%20to%20those%20people%20that%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20government%20had%20said%20%E2%80%93%20that%20Muslims%20have%20the%20first%20right%20to%20the%20nation's%20wealth%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20the%20Congress%20manifesto%20promise%20to%20redistribute%20wealth%3F%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20manifesto%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20makes%20several%20statements%20regarding%20income%20inequality%2C%20India's%20wealth%2C%20people%20belonging%20to%20economically%20weak%20sections%2C%20and%20the%20allocation%20of%20government%20land%20and%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20will%20conduct%20a%20nationwide%20Socio-Economic%20and%20Caste%20Census%20to%20enumerate%20the%20castes%20and%20sub-castes%20and%20their%20socio-economic%20conditions.%20Based%20on%20the%20data%2C%20we%20will%20strengthen%20the%20agenda%20for%20affirmative%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20one%20of%20the%20points%20in%20the%20manifesto%2C%20called%20the%20'Nyay%20Patra'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20point%2C%20the%20Congress%20says%20%26quot%3BThe%20economic%20empowerment%20of%20minorities%20is%20a%20necessary%20step%20for%20India%20to%20realise%20its%20full%20potential.%20We%20will%20ensure%20that%20banks%20will%20provide%20institutional%20credit%20to%20minorities%20without%20discrimination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20nowhere%20in%20their%20manifesto%20does%20the%20Congress%20claim%20that%20it%20will%20seize%20the%20wealth%20from%20the%20rich%20and%20distribute%20it%20among%20the%20poor.%20The%20party%20has%20promised%20a%20caste%20census%20to%20gather%20data%2C%20and%20accordingly%20implement%20affirmative%20action%20policy.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20called%20the%20census%20an%20'X-ray'%20of%20India%20which%20the%20party%20believes%20will%20aid%20them%20in%20policy%20making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party's%20manifesto%20adds%20that%20it%20will%20%26quot%3Baddress%20the%20growing%20inequality%20of%20wealth%20and%20income%20through%20suitable%20changes%20in%20policies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manifesto%20also%20mentions%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20charge%26quot%3B%20on%20resources%20in%20a%20point%20under%20the%20'Welfare'%20section.%20It%20mentions%20that%20India%20has%20%26quot%3Bnearly%2022%20crore%20people%20who%20are%20poor%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20under%20their%20governance%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20welfare%20of%20the%20poor%20will%20be%20the%20first%20charge%20on%20all%20government%20resources.%26quot%3B%20But%20it%20makes%20no%20statements%20regarding%20surveying%20gold%20owned%20by%20Indian%20women%20or%20about%20restributing%20the%20'surveyed'%20wea%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Did%20Sam%20Pitroda%20Say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESam%20Pitroda%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Indian%20Overseas%20Congress%2C%20said%20that%20India%20should%20discuss%20bringing%20a%20policy%20similar%20to%20the%20inheritance%20tax%20where%20the%20government%20takes%2055%20per%20cent%20of%20a%20person's%20wealth%20after%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20person%20has%20property%20worth%20US%20dollars%2010%20million%2C%20then%20after%20his%20death%2C%2045%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20property%20goes%20to%20his%20children%20and%2055%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20property%20goes%20to%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pitroda%20told%20ANI%20and%20added%20that%20there%20is%20no%20such%20law%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20issues%20should%20be%20discussed.%20We%20are%20talking%20about%20policies%20that%20are%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20people%2C%20not%20just%20the%20rich%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Chicago%2C%20US%3A%20Chairman%20of%20Indian%20Overseas%20Congress%2C%20Sam%20Pitroda%20says%2C%20%26quot%3B...This%20is%20a%20policy%20issue.%20Congress%20party%20would%20frame%20a%20policy%20through%20which%20the%20wealth%20distribution%20would%20be%20better...We%20don't%20have%20a%20minimum%20wage%20(in%20India)...If%20we%20come%20up%20with%20a%20minimum%20wage%20in%20the%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPO6Mnili5p%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FPO6Mnili5p%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1782960588252963222%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2024%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worth%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20US%20does%20not%20have%20a%20federal%20inheritance%20tax.%20In%20some%20states%2C%20such%20as%20Iowa%2C%20Kentucky%2C%20Maryland%2C%20Nebraska%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20and%20Pennsylvania%2C%20inherited%20assets%20are%20taxed.%20The%20payable%20tax%20depends%20on%20the%20amount%20of%20the%20inheritance%20and%20the%20relationship%20to%20the%20dead.%20This%20tax%20is%20only%20applied%20above%20a%20certain%20threshold%20and%20can%20go%20up%20to%20nearly%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20inheritance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20Congress%20Say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Congress%20leaders%20have%20come%20out%20and%20clarified%20that%20there%20are%20no%20plans%20of%20'seizing%20and%20redistributing'%20wealth%20if%20they%20are%20voted%20to%20power%20in%20the%202024%20elections.%20The%20party%20has%20also%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20highlighting%20PM%20Modi's%20speech.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Sam%20Pitroda's%20recent%20remarks%20have%20forced%20the%20party%20into%20firefighting%20mode%20saying%20that%20the%20comments%20do%20not%20reflect%20the%20party's%20policies%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Pitroda's%20views%20always%20reflect%20the%20position%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress.%20Many%20times%20they%20do%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20in%20a%20tweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESam%20Pitroda%20has%20been%20a%20mentor%2C%20friend%2C%20philosopher%2C%20and%20guide%20to%20many%20across%20the%20world%2C%20including%20me.%20He%20has%20made%20numerous%2C%20enduring%20contributions%20to%20India's%20developments.%20He%20is%20President%20of%20the%20Indian%20Overseas%20Congress.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMr%20Pitroda%20expresses%20his%20opinions%20freely%20on%20issues%20he%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1782991143099318694%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2024%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Fresh%20Attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeading%20the%20BJP's%20attack%20over%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Sam%20Pitroda's%20comments%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20alleged%20that%20the%20Opposition%20party%20plans%20to%20tax%20inheritance%20passed%20down%20from%20parents%20to%20their%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20poll%20rally%20at%20Chhattisgarh's%20Surguja%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20Congress's%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%20intentions%20are%20coming%20out%20in%20the%20open%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20wealth%20you%20accumulate%20with%20your%20hard%20work%20won't%20pass%20down%20to%20your%20children.%20The%20Congress's%20hand%20will%20snatch%20it.%20The%20Congress's%20mantra%20is%20'loot%20during%20your%20lifetime%2C%20loot%20after%20your%20death'%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713947160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F0791f43k_congress-manifesto_625x300_24_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsam-pitroda-controversy-bjp-vs-congress-congress-manifesto-has-congress-promised-wealth-redistribution-in-manifesto-a-fact-check-5511606%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20huge%20political%20row%20has%20broken%20out%20over%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Sam%20Pitroda's%20remarks%20on%20inheritance%20tax%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20claiming%20that%20this%20was%20a%20sign%20that%20the%20party%2C%20if%20voted%20to%20power%2C%20will%20redistribute%20the%20wealth%20of%20Indians.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fi