%3Cp%3EIt%20has%C2%A0been%20200%20days%20since%20Israel%20launched%20its%20brutal%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20retaliating%20against%20the%20October%207%20attack%20carried%20out%20by%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20calls%20for%20the%20ceasefire%20grow%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20university%20and%20college%20students%20in%20the%20US%20have%20also%20launched%20protests%20demanding%20an%20end%20to%C2%A0Israel's%C2%A0military%20campaign%20that%20has%20killed%20over%2034%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20US%20University%20Students%20Are%20Protesting%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20across%20the%20US%20universities%20and%20colleges%20have%20been%20holding%20sit-ins%20to%20register%20their%20protest%20against%20not%20just%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%20but%20also%20the%20US's%20continuous%20support%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20calling%20for%20a%20permanent%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%2C%20students%20have%20demanded%20an%20end%20to%20US%20military%20assistance%20for%20Israel%2C%20and%C2%A0university%20divestment%20--%20withdrawal%20of%20stocks%2C%20bonds%2C%20or%20investment%20funds%20from%20arms%20suppliers%20and%20companies%20benefitting%20from%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20demands%20also%20include%20reprieve%20for%20students%20and%20faculty%20members%20disciplined%20or%20fired%20for%20protesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20Protests%20Anti-Semitism%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20pro-Palestine%20protests%20have%20taken%20centre%C2%A0stage%2C%20several%20Jewish%20student%20groups%20have%20labelled%20these%20demonstrations%20as%20%26quot%3Banti-semitism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20claim%20that%20the%20pro-Palestine%20protests%20are%20against%20Israel%20and%20Zionism%2C%20which%20calls%20for%20a%20separate%20Jewish%20state%20on%20the%20Palestinian%20lands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20these%20claims%20have%20been%20dismissed%20by%20pro-Palestine%20protesters%2C%20who%20said%20there%20was%20a%20clear%20distinction%20between%20anti-Zionist%2Fanti-Israel%20views%20and%20antisemitism.%20They%20say%20being%20anti-Israel%20or%20anti-zionism%20--%20calling%20for%20a%20Jewish-exclusive%20state%20--%20was%20not%20the%20same%20as%20anti-semitism%2C%20which%20means%20the%20hatred%20for%20and%20of%20all%20Jews.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20Protests%20Have%20Affected%20Campus%20Life%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Columbia%20University%2C%20the%20protests%20have%20contributed%20to%20high%20tensions%20on%20campus%2C%20with%20some%20students%20fearful%20about%20attending%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20varsity%20has%20announced%20that%20they%20will%20switch%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Flive-blog%2Fcampus-protests-palestine-gaza-live-updates-rcna148925%5C%22%3Ehybrid%20learning%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20semester.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20State%20Polytechnic%20University's%20campus%20will%20remain%20closed%20until%20Wednesday%20due%20to%20protesters%20occupying%20a%20building%20on%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20University%20is%20concerned%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20students%20who%20remain%20in%20the%20building%2C%20and%20has%20been%20asking%20the%20students%20to%20remain%20open%20to%20dialogue%20around%20a%20peaceful%20resolution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.humboldt.edu%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3Evarsity%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClasses%20are%20cancelled%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20evacuation%20of%20students%2C%20faculty%2C%20and%20employees%20from%20five%20ongoing%20courses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20shut%20down%20the%20building%20after%20protesters%20disrupted%20classes%2C%20and%20university%20operations%2C%20and%20vandalised%20university%20property.%20They%20have%20incorporated%20remote%20work%20and%20In-p