ans%20to%20tax%20inheritance%20passed%20down%20from%20parents%20to%20their%20children.%20The%20Congress%20has%20distanced%20itself%20from%20Mr%20Pitroda's%20remarks%20and%20said%20they%20do%20not%20reflect%20the%20party's%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20poll%20rally%20at%20Chhattisgarh's%20Surguja%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20Congress's%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%20intentions%20are%20coming%20out%20in%20the%20open%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Mr%20Pitroda%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20advisor%20of%20the%20prince%20of%20the%20Congress%20royal%20family%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20the%20middle%20class%20should%20be%20taxed%20more.%20Now%20they%20have%20gone%20further%20ahead.%20Now%20the%20Congress%20is%20saying%20that%20it%20will%20impose%20an%20Inheritance%20Tax%20and%20tax%20the%20inheritance%20received%20by%20people%20from%20their%20parents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20wealth%20you%20accumulate%20with%20your%20hard%20work%20won't%20pass%20down%20to%20your%20children.%20The%20Congress's%20hand%20will%20snatch%20it.%20The%20Congress's%20mantra%20is%20'loot%20during%20your%20lifetime%2C%20loot%20after%20your%20death'%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20taking%20a%20cue%20from%20Life%20Insurance%20Corporation's%20%26quot%3Bzindagi%20ke%20saath%20bhi%2C%20zindagi%20ke%20baad%20bhi%26quot%3B%20tagline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20you%20live%2C%20Congress's%20high%20taxation%20will%20make%20you%20suffer.%20When%20you%20are%20dead%2C%20they%20will%20put%20the%20burden%20of%20inheritance%20tax%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pitroda%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20overseas%20wing%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20huge%20row%20after%20his%20remarks%20during%20an%20interview%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI.%20While%20targeting%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20over%20his%20allegations%20that%20the%20Congress%20plans%20to%20redistribute%20the%20nation's%20wealth%20and%20that%20will%20take%20property%20and%20jewellery%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20power%2C%20Mr%20Pitroda%20said%20the%20Congress's%20manifesto%20is%20well-drafted%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20making%20up%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20always%20focused%20on%20the%20people%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20economic%20pyramid%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20OBCs%2C%20Muslims%2C%20Dalits%20or%20tribals.%20%26quot%3BBillionaires%20don't%20need%20our%20help.%20It%20is%20the%20poor%20people%20who%20need%20our%20help.%20Inequality%20has%20substantially%20increased%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20you%20are%20going%20to%20take%20your%20wealth%20and%20give%20it%20to%20somebody.%20This%20means%20to%20create%20new%20policies%20so%20that%20the%20concentration%20of%20wealth%20can%20be%20prevented.%20It's%20like%20a%20Monopoly%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20cited%20a%20US%20example%20that%20snowballed%20into%20a%20controversy.%20%26quot%3BIn%20America%2C%20there%20is%20an%20inheritance%20tax.%20If%20one%20has%20100%20million%20USD%20worth%20of%20wealth%20and%20when%20he%20dies%20he%20can%20only%20transfer%20probably%2045%20per%20cent%20to%20his%20children%2C%2055%20per%20cent%20is%20grabbed%20by%20the%20government.%20That's%20an%20interesting%20law.%20It%20says%20you%20in%20your%20generation%2C%20made%20wealth%20and%20you%20are%20leaving%20now%2C%20you%20must%20leave%20your%20wealth%20for%20the%20public%2C%20not%20all%20of%20it%2C%20half%20of%20it%2C%20which%20to%20me%20sounds%20fair%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pitroda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worth%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20US%20does%20not%20have%20a%20federal%20inheritance%20tax.%20In%20some%20states%2C%20such%20as%20Iowa%2C%20Kentucky%2C%20Maryland%2C%20Nebraska%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20and%20Pennsylvania%2C%20inherited%20assets%20are%20taxed.%20The%20payable%20tax%20depends%20on%20the%20amount%20of%20the%20inheritance%20and%20the%20relationship%20to%20the%20dead.%20This%20tax%20is%20only%20applied%20above%20a%20certain%20threshold%20and%20can%20go%20up%20to%20nearly%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20inheritance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pitroda%20said%20this%20is%20a%20policy%20issue.%20%26quot%3BCongress%20party%20would%20frame%20a%20policy%20through%20which%20the%20wealth%20distribution%20would%20be%20better.%20We%20don't%20have%20a%20minimum%20wage%20(in%20India).%20If%20we%20come%20up%20with%20a%20minimum%20wage%20in%20the%20country%20saying%20you%20must%20pay%20so%20much%20money%20to%20the%20poor%2C%20that's%20the%20distribution%20of%20wealth.%20Today%2C%20rich%20people%20don't%20pay%20their%20peons%2C%20servants%2C%20and%20home%20help%20enough%2C%20but%20they%20spend%20that%20money%20on%20a%20vacation%20in%20Dubai%20and%20London%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20remarks%20started%20doing%20the%20rounds%20on%20social%20media%2C%20the%20BJP%20doubled%20up%20on%20its%20charge%20against%20the%20Congress.%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20appealed%20to%20the%20people%20to%20take%20Mr%20Pitroda's%20remarks%20seriously.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20hidden%20plans%20have%20come%20out%20in%20the%20open.%20People%20should%20take%20note.%20And%20the%20Congress%20must%20withdraw%20the%20mention%20of%20survey%20from%20its%20manifesto%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20manifesto%20calls%20for%20a%20nationwide%20socio-economic%20and%20caste%20Census%20to%20provide%20the%20data%20foundation%20for%20affirmative%20action%2C%20but%20does%20not%20mention%20any%20wealth%20redistribution%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20has%20gained%20steam%20after%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20alleged%20in%20election%20rallies%20that%20the%20Congress%20plans%20to%20conduct%20a%20survey%20and%20put%20into%20motion%20a%20wealth%20redistribution%20plan.%20He%20has%20also%20claimed%20that%20property%20and%20jewellery%20owned%20by%20citizens%20would%20be%20surveyed%2C%20taken%20away%20and%20redistibuted.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPushed%20into%20firefighting%20mode%20over%20Mr%20Pitroda's%20remarks%2C%20the%20Congress%20distanced%20itself%20from%20the%20senior%20leader's%20remark%20and%20stressed%20that%20its%20manifesto%20does%20not%20mention%20what%20the%20BJP%20is%20alleging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BSam%20Pitroda%20has%20been%20a%20mentor%2C%20friend%2C%20philosopher%2C%20and%20guide%20to%20many%20across%20the%20world%2C%20including%20me.%20He%20has%20made%20numerous%2C%20enduring%20contributions%20to%20India's%20developments.%20He%20is%20President%20of%20the%20Indian%20Overseas%20Congress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Pitroda%20expresses%20his%20opinions%20freely%20on%20issues%20he%20feels%20strongly%20about.%20Surely%2C%20in%20a%20democracy%20an%20individual%20is%20at%20liberty%20to%20discuss%2C%20express%2C%20and%20debate%20his%20personal%20views.%20This%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20Mr.%20Pitroda's%20views%20always%20reflect%20the%20position%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress.%20Many%20times%20they%20do%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramesh%20clarified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSensationalising%20his%20comments%20now%20and%20tearing%20them%20out%20of%20context%20are%20deliberate%20and%20desperate%20attempts%20at%20diverting%20attention%20away%20from%20Mr.%20Narendra%20Modi's%20malicious%20and%20mischievous%20election%20campaign%3B%20that%20is%20anchored%20ONLY%20in%20lies%20and%20more%20lies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawan%20Khera%2C%20chairman%20of%20Congress's%20media%20and%20publicity%20department%2C%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20remarks%20suggest%20that%20he%20has%20a%20problem%20with%20social%20justice.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20the%20society's%20deprived%20section%20has%20been%20left%20far%20behind%20due%20to%20Mr%20Modi's%20policies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20Mr%20Pitroda%20had%20not%20said%20the%20Congress%20will%20bring%20any%20inheritance%20act%20policy%20and%20that%20no%20such%20policy%20is%20mentioned%20in%20the%20party's%20manifesto%2C%20he%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20discussing%20and%20debating%20different%20ideas%20not%20allowed%20in%20this%20ancient%20land%20of%20Shastrarth%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20spokesperson%20Supriya%20Shrinate%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20party%20did%20not%20impose%20any%20inheritance%20tax%20when%20it%20was%20in%20power%20for%20so%20many%20years.%20%26quot%3BNow%20you%20are%20trying%20to%20spread%20lies%20and%20create%20a%20bogey%20when%20there%20is%20none%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20doesn't%20believe%20in%20inheritance%20tax%20and%20we%20have%20never%20discussed%20or%20contemplated%20this.%20It's%20actually%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20former%20finance%20minister%20Arun%20Jaitley%20who%20contemplated%20this%2C%20it's%20their%20agenda%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713943320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F0g2pk3ho_sam-pitroda-remarks_625x300_24_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-loots-people-even-after-death-pm-slams-sam-pitrodas-comment-5511162%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Leading%20the%20BJP's%20attack%20over%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Sam%20Pitroda's%20comments%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20alleged%20that%20the%20Opposition%20party%20plans%20to%20tax%20inheritance%20passed%20down%20from%20parents%20to%20their%20children%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-loots-people-even-after-death-pm-slams-sam-pitrodas-comment-5511162%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.amppr