%20India%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%3B%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%3B%20and%20other%20Government%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETesting%20your%20mental%20and%20physical%20fitness%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20preparing%20and%20getting%20the%20necessary%20permissions%20from%20the%20two%20Governments%2C%20the%20Navy%20and%20the%20Coast%20Guard%2C%20the%20two%20swimmers%20left%20for%20Sri%20Lanka%20from%20Dhanushkodi%20on%2013%20April%2C%202024%2C%20by%20boat.%20The%20boat%20ride%20itself%20was%20challenging%20and%20led%20to%20severe%20motion%20sickness.%20They%20slept%20on%20the%20boat%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-18-at-11.45.04-min-1713870887-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20duo%20aim%20to%20promote%20adventure%20sports%20and%20open%20water%20swimming%20in%20India.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-18-at-11.45.04-min-1713870887-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-18-at-11.45.04-min-1713870887-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-18-at-11.45.04-min-1713870887-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-18-at-11.45.04-min-1713870887-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-18-at-11.45.04-min-1713870887-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-18-at-11.45.04-min-1713870887-150x200.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.t