%20land%20among%20the%20stars%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20borrowing%20from%20this%20philosophy%2C%20Samyak%20says%20in%20his%20second%20attempt%2C%20he%20kept%20the%20general%20category%20cut-off%20as%20his%20goal%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20PwD%20(persons%20with%20disabilities)%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20the%20PwD%20category%20has%20a%20lower%20cut-off%20than%20the%20general.%20In%20my%20first%20attempt%2C%20I%20had%20noticed%20this%20and%20was%20trying%20to%20match%20this%20cut-off.%20But%2C%20in%20my%20second%20attempt%2C%20I%20learnt%20from%20my%20mistake%20and%20aimed%20for%20the%20general%20category%20cut-off.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFind%20a%20holy%20grail%20for%20your%20optional%20subject%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreparing%20for%20the%20UPSC%20is%20often%20viewed%20as%20nerve-racking%20by%20the%20many%20aspirants%20who%20attempt%20it%20every%20year.%20But%20a%20foolproof%20plan%20is%20what%20will%20differentiate%20you%20from%20others%2C%20believes%20Samyak.%20While%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F307829%2Frevision-tips-for-upsc-cse-mains-optional-subject-by-ias-officer-akshita-gupta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echoosing%20an%20optional%20subject%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20recommends%20going%20for%20something%20that%20you%20are%20passionate%20about%20and%20know%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20political%20science%20and%20international%20relations%20from%20JNU%20(Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20Delhi)%20formed%20the%20basis%20for%20Samyak%20choosing%20political%20science%20and%20international%20relations%20as%20his%20optional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotes%20formed%20the%20bedrock%20of%20his%20preparation%20strategy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20political%20science%20paper%2C%20Samyak%20says%20it%20is%20divided%20into%20two%20parts%2C%20with%20each%20part%20featuring%20two%20sections.%20Out%20of%20the%20four%20sections%2C%20three%20are%20static%20(a%20set%20of%20questions%20that%20repeat%20over%20the%20years)%20and%20one%20is%20dynamic%20(questions%20that%20assess%20your%20knowledge%20of%20current%20affairs%20and%20news).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20static%20sections%2C%20going%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F277424%2Fbest-books-for-upsc-cse-indian-polity-laxmikanth-amazon%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevious%20years%E2%80%99%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%20suffices%2C%20Samyak%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20question%20bank%20(of%20notes)%20has%20around%202%2C500%20questions%20that%20feature%20ad%20verbatim%2C%20with%20a%20few%20changes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20This%20leaves%20a%20candidate%20with%20the%20fourth%20section%20on%20which%20they%20must%20spend%20adequate%20time.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20section%20is%20more%20challenging%20than%20the%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20Samyak%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECoaching%20might%20not%20be%20your%20cup%20of%20tea%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamyak%20once%20harboured%20a%20dream%20to%20become%20an%20engineer.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20phase%20when%20he%20was%20preparing%20for%20the%20IIT%20exam%20that%20he%20attended%20coaching%20classes.%20However%2C%20he%20instantly%20knew%20this%20style%20of%20learning%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20suited%20to%20his%20temperament.%20Thus%2C%20when%20it%20came%20to%20the%20UPSC%20exam%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20study%20by%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20wanting%20to%20dissuade%20anyone%20from%20opting%20for%20coaching%2C%20Samyak%20emphasises%20it%20merely%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20his%20cup%20of%20tea.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20each%20his%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reiterates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAcing%20the%20final%20frontier%20%E2%80%94%20the%20personality%20test%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20part%20of%20the%20daunting%20UPSC%20exam%20%E2%80%9